---------------------------------------------------------------------
Models Implemented :

TF-IDF + Logistic Regression
1) Classical ML baseline
2) Fast inference
3) Interpretable

LSTM (PyTorch)
1)Word-level tokenization
2)Sequence-based sentiment learning

DistilBERT - 
1)Transformer-based
2)High accuracy
3)Fine-tuned for sentiment classification
------------------------------------------------------------

FastAPI -
Start API Server

uvicorn src.api.app:app --reload

Available Endpoints
POST /predict
{
  "text": "The movie was amazing",
  "model": "bert"
}
Response
{
  "sentiment": "positive",
  "confidence": 0.97,
  "model_used": "distilbert"
}
Supported models: - logistic - bert - lstm
----------------------------------------------------------

