----------------------------------------------------------

Streamlit Application -
Run Streamlit App :
streamlit run src/chatbot/streamlit_chatbot.py

Features :
Text input
Model selection (Logistic / LSTM / BERT)
GPT-based explanation
Optional dataset insight
Clean UI

Testing (PyTest) :
Run API tests-
pytest src/tests/test_api.py -v
Tests include: - Valid predictions - Invalid model handling - Health endpoint - Metrics endpoint

-----------------------------------------------------------------------
requirement -
pip -r install requirements.txt

Explainability -

GPT4All generates human-readable explanations
Keyword-based reasoning
Dataset-level insights from IMDb reviews



